Description:
In the southwest sector of Calgary, you can find a Spiritleaf Cannabis Shop in Millrise! This suburban neighbourhood is found west of Macleod Trail and south of Fish Creek Provincial Park. The area offers access to the cities light rail transit (LRT) system, which takes commuters straight into the heart of downtown and beyond. Its population hovers around 7,000 residents, with 80’s style housing and plenty of condominiums. There is also a community garden and an ice skating rink to enjoy. Nearby, locals and visitors can explore Fish Creek Provincial Park Pathways and day-use areas, featuring plenty of local wildlife and native plants. There in the park is the Bow Valley Ranche Restaurant, one of the best restaurants in Calgary. Fostering true community spirit in the prairie province of Alberta.

Spiritleaf aims to be the most knowledgeable and trusted recreational cannabis shop. We believe in connecting people in a world which is deeply divided. We believe that everyone matters equally, regardless of status, age, ethnicity or creed. We aim to foster true community spirit through what we stand for, who we serve and the products we provide.
